Overcast sky.  Light breeze- 45 degrees- 32 degrees this am.
Slight southerly breeze- overcast sky- 1.2" rain in the last 2 days.
Water green due to tree pollen on surface.  Clear- slight breeze- temp.-70 degrees.
Clear- breezy- chop on water- temp. in 60s.
Cloudy- light breeze- windy last 2 days.
Partly sunny- breezy- water quite choppy.
Cloudy- slight S breeze- thunderstorms around.
Mostly clear.  T. shower earlier- slight breeze- some algae starting.
Light overcast- little breeze- some algae.
Clear- bright sun- no breeze- some algae.

Clear- calm and sunny- had 9.5" of rain on the 14th -16th.
Clear- sunny- north breeze.  Had 1.75" rain on the 8th + 9th.
Mostly sunny-southwest breeze 15 mph-slight chop on water.
Partly cloudy- south breeze- humid- high 80's.
Mostly cloudy-light NE breeze-no rain recently.
Overcast-no breeze-more algae present also floating weeds.
Mostly clear- 10 mph SE breeze- 4" rain 24th through 27th.
Clear- sunny- slight SW breeze- +28 this a.m.
Mostly cloudy- brisk SW breeze- temp. high 30's.
Clear- NW breeze 10 mph- ice out April 29-30th.
Clear- sunny- slight west breeze- no rain for over a week- slight frost last night.
Clear- sunny- NW breeze- still some pollen S end of lake.
Mostly clear. NW breeze 15 mph. .35" rain last evening.
Cloudy- NE breeze 10 mph- 4.1 in. rain on 17th and 18th.
Partly cloudy- NW breeze 10 mph- temp. 70s.
Mostly cloudy- slight west breeze- temp. low 60's.
Cold. mostly clear- slight NE breeze. fish not biting. beavers have outlet dammed.
Partly sunny- S breeze- temp. 67 degrees. ice out 4/19/97.

Mostly sunny- N breeze 15 mph. temp. mid 60's- need rain.

Partly cloudy- light variable breeze- temp. high 70's.
Mostly sunny- slight W breeze- temp = high 70's.
Clear with a light northwest breeze.  Ice out was on 4/2/98.
Mostly clear with a northerly breeze.  There was frost this morning.

Mostly clear with high clouds and a northeast breeze.
Mostly clear with a light southeast breeze.
Mostly clear with a light northwest breeze.
Mostly sunny with a westerly breeze.
Cloudy with a southwest breeze.  Temperature highs in the 50's.
Cloudy with a northwest breeze.  Temperature in the 50's.
Clear and sunny with a southwest breeze.  Temperature in the 60's.
Clear SW breeze- air temp low 60's- ice out 04/06- wood duck nest boxes put out 04/01.
Clear- calm.- temp hi 60's- orioles arrived 05/11- baby geese on 05/16- hummers 05/12.
Mostly cloudy- lt. SE breeze- thunderheads developing- temp hi 60's.
Mostly clear evening.  25th had 5.0" rain with high winds.  Still 24 geese on lake.
Mostly clear- SE breeze 15 mph- water looks more brown than green.
Mostly clear.  Sw breeze 10 mph.  Frost morning of 21st.  Temp 48 F.
Clear- light south breeze.  Temp 45 F. 27 F this am.  Last reading for 1999.
Outside temperature was 67 degrees F- partly sunny- water temperature was 57 degrees F.
My grandson Logan helped with the reading.
Beautiful late summer day- no wind.
More algae in water than last reading.
Sun showing through after rainfall most of the day.
Bright- clear day after the big storm

Water Calm- some algae blooms. Water temp 77

Lot of rain this week- this will be my last reading for 2019! Headed south! See ys next spring! Be Well- Ray
